{"tid":1157576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"乘客公審青年男女唔讓座 網民反問：一定要讓？","createTime":"2019-05-16T11:34:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T11:37:59.000Z","uid":72009,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5031f47ef1e370ea92c5fa40bf9ac37328469010","tid":1157576,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"「關愛座」變成「批鬥座」已經不是甚麼新鮮事，甚至網絡上已經有不少人反批鬥那些喜歡公審不讓座行為的網民，日前就再有西鐵乘客於網上公審一對青年男女不願意讓座，最後落得反被批鬥的下場。<br />\n<br />\n早前有一位西鐵乘客於 Facebook 群組「元朗吹水區」發帖，指坐西鐵時目睹一對青年男女不願讓座。事主指當日有一對長者於柯士甸站上車，並站在一對青年男女的面前，他形容其中一名老翁「連手都舉不起」，要扶著身邊的婆婆才能站穩，不過該對年青男女無動於衷。<br />\n<br />\n事主看不過眼，上前詢問對方能否讓座，豈料該對男女卻以粗口惡言相向，拒絕讓座，並繼續高談闊論。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/05/16/9/9df37147f314dbe9677ec1f028049653.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2F9%2F9df37147f314dbe9677ec1f028049653.jpg&h=c216b3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/05/16/2/29a1491ee3bb4844f04020799762dde9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2F2%2F29a1491ee3bb4844f04020799762dde9.jpg&h=867b7a00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/9/2019/05/16/d/dd249e2e9ae7b682ba6392b0d0eae848.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F9%2F2019%2F05%2F16%2Fd%2Fdd249e2e9ae7b682ba6392b0d0eae848.jpg&h=f28db567&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾多過老野咁多，不讓"},{"pid":"2a060d6fef03ca9fbc188181e7ee7efcb5dd2a5d","tid":1157576,"uid":5499,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T11:37:59.000Z","msg":"想坐就答的士啦"}]}